e:["$","p","10",{"className":"text-[17.5px] leading-8 text-neutral-800","children":"A simple approach is to divide your income into essentials, savings, and discretionary spending. The exact percentages matter less than the habit itself. As long as you consistently spend less than you earn and save something every month, your financial position will gradually improve."}]
