20:["$","p","28",{"className":"text-[17.5px] leading-8 text-neutral-800","children":"Investing is essential for long-term wealth because it helps your money grow faster than inflation. Keeping all your money in cash may feel safe, but inflation slowly reduces purchasing power over time."}]
