27:["$","p","35",{"className":"text-[17.5px] leading-8 text-neutral-800","children":"While saving and investing are powerful, increasing income can significantly accelerate wealth building. This does not necessarily mean working longer hours, but working smarter."}]
28:["$","p","36",{"className":"text-[17.5px] leading-8 text-neutral-800","children":"Improving skills, negotiating salary, freelancing, consulting, or making strategic career changes can increase earning potential. The key is ensuring that income increases are not immediately consumed by higher spending."}]
