35:["$","p","49",{"className":"text-[17.5px] leading-8 text-neutral-800","children":"Building wealth is a process built on small, consistent actions. It does not require perfection, luck, or a high income. It requires awareness, discipline, and time."}]
36:["$","p","50",{"className":"text-[17.5px] leading-8 text-neutral-800","children":"By controlling expenses, saving consistently, eliminating high-interest debt, investing patiently, and planning for the future, anyone can create long-term financial security. The most important step is simply starting and staying committed over time."}]
